frs.broker.ipc.http

Class UriTunnelServerRequestHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • frs.broker.ipc.http.UriTunnelServerRequestHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServerRequestHandler

    public class UriTunnelServerRequestHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServerRequestHandler
    ServerRequestHandler implementation using HTTP and URI Tunneling. NOTE! Spark-Java likes static methods too much which are contradictionary to flexible delegation based designs as their bindings are made too early. You therefore have to A) Instantiate the SRH and next B) invoke the srh.registerRoutes() method.

    Implementation based on the Spark-Java framework.
